author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Vitruvio Real Estate Assets Valued At 107 Mln Euros At End Of FY
text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - VITRUVIO REAL ESTATE SOCIMI SA:
* SAID ON THURSDAY ASSET VALUATION AT END-DECEMBER AT OVER 170 MILLION EUROS, UP 3.9 PCT VERSUS VALUATION AT JUNE 30, 2017
* NAV PER SHARE AT END-DECEMBER AT14.26 EUROS Source text: bit.ly/2FYNV7B bit.ly/2nU7uXu
